  "original_title": "\u0d86\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dae\u0dd2\u0d9a \u0d85\u0db7\u0dd2\u0dba\u0ddd\u0d9c \u0dad\u0dd4\u0dc5 \u0d8b\u0dc3\u0dc3\u0dca \u0d85\u0db0\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0dcf\u0db4\u0db1\u0dba\u0da7 \u0db8\u0dd6\u0dbd\u0dca\u200d\u0dba \u0dc3\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Financial support for higher education in times of economic challenges",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Moneta has introduced the 'Study Now, Pay Later' solution in collaboration with Achievers Lanka Business School, a leader in Sri Lanka's higher education sector.",
        "Accordingly, through the mobile app under the Moneta brand of Fintech Hive private company, students can get financial support for their professional education or higher education, and they have the opportunity to repay the amount without interest in 4 installments.",
        "There, students have the opportunity to acquire qualifications such as CIM, CIMA and ACCA, and because this service uses state-of-the-art digital technologies including artificial intelligence, financial service requests can be completed within 10 minutes without long paperwork or queues. Says it can. This application can be downloaded from Google Play and App Store.",
        "Present at the launch were Achievers Lanka Business School Chairman Azad Hai, Manager (Academics & Operations) Amar Aufar, Business Head Anushan Sadanandasarma, Manager (Marketing & Sales) Amjad Maulana, Group Accountant Ajurdeen Azharuddin and Moneta Founder & CEO Kanaganayagam Shayanthan. , Mr. Randu Perera, Business Development Manager participated."
      ],
